ScraperBelt\\ScrapeLogger\\ZipRotatingFi.docblock:
Extends Symfony's RotatingFileHandler to create a gzipped copy of the log file before removing it.
Stores logs to files that are rotated every day and a limited number of files are kept…
… unzipped.
